<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ ạ̹lhy nạdi qlby</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (yạ ạ̹lhy nạdi qlby fậty ạ̹lyk
 yạ ạ̹lhy ạ̉nt qrby wsẖwqy ạ̹lyk)2
 (kạsẖtyạq ạlʿṭsẖy̱ fy ạlṣḥrạʾ lmạʾ
 ṣrkẖty ạ̉yạ nbʿy ạ̉ryd ạrtwạʾ)2
 2- (kl mạ fy ḥyạty bdwnk mwạt
 ḍḥkạty kdmʿạty hn bạhtạt)2
 (ạ̉y mʿnaⁿy̱ gẖyrk fy ạlḥyạẗ ạ̉ḥyạ fyh
 ạ̉nt mʿny̱ ạlmʿny̱ fy kl ḥyạty ạ̉rtjyh)2
 3- (fy ẓlạmy lạ ạ̉ryḥ ạ̉ḥd wlạ ạ̉stryḥ
 wậlạmy kʿdẖạb ạlsfn fy ʿṣf ryḥ)2
 (lạ tdʿny ạ̉ḥyạ fy ẓlmty llậbạd
 rdny lạ tdʿny ạ̉mwt fy ạbtʿạd)2
 4- (thdạ̉ rwḥy fy ạlḥḍn bl ạ̉nạm
 mṭmỷnaⁿạ ʿly̱ ṣdrk ạlḥnwn fy slạm)2
 (yạ ạ̉by kyf ywṣf ḥbk ạlʿjyb
 yạ ạ̉by qlby ṭạb fy ḥḍnk ạlrḥyb)2</lyrics>
<hymn_number>11093</hymn_number>
<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
</song>